    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and is currently in running order. While the engine and transmission are functional, the car shows signs of age, including some minor exterior scratches and interior wear on the upholstery. It serves as reliable basic transportation, though a buyer should expect to address some minor mechanical maintenance and cosmetic touch-ups in the near future. The electrical system is mostly functional, with only a few minor quirks typical for its age.",
