    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this expertly maintained vehicle, currently offered in commendable condition. This unit has undergone a thorough professional inspection to ensure that its mechanical systems and aesthetic appointments meet our exacting standards. Representing a sophisticated balance of performance and long-term value, this vehicle is an ideal acquisition for the discerning driver who demands reliability without compromise.",
      "price": 33850.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 30
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and it\u2019s honestly been such a joy to own. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-loved, so it\u2019s ready to hit the road with its next owner right away! It runs super smoothly and looks great parked in the driveway. If you're looking for a dependable car that still has plenty of life left, this is the one for you. Feel free to reach out if you want to come by and take it for a spin!",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 30
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available for the discerning driver is a 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine and a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission. This chassis has been meticulously maintained with a focus on mechanical longevity; the Vanos system has been overhauled and the rear subframe\u2014a known weak point\u2014has been professionally reinforced. The engine utilizes its factory individual throttle bodies to deliver linear power up to an 8,000 RPM redline. Handling is sharp thanks to a limited-slip differential and refreshed suspension bushings. While the exterior shows minor patina consistent with a well-loved driver's car, the drivetrain and structural components are track-ready and mechanically sound.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 30
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "2018 Sedan. Good condition. Well-maintained. Clean title. Runs smooth.",
      "price": 28500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 30
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained 2019 Audi A6 55 TFSI Quattro, finished in a timeless Manhattan Gray Metallic. This vehicle has been garage-kept and primarily used for highway commuting, ensuring the mechanical components have been treated with care. The exterior retains a deep, glossy luster; while there are a few minor stone chips on the front bumper consistent with regular use, the body is free of any major dents or deep scratches. Inside, the Valcona leather interior remains supple and smoke-free. The dual-screen MMI touch response system is fully functional, and the Bang & Olufsen 3D Premium Sound System delivers crisp audio performance. Mechanically, this car is robust. I have adhered to a strict maintenance schedule, with the most recent service including a full synthetic oil change, new cabin air filters, and a brake fluid flush. The tires have approximately 70% tread remaining, and the transmission shifts seamlessly through all gears. All original manuals, two key fobs, and a folder of service receipts are included. This is a solid, honest example of a luxury sedan that balances performance with everyday reliability.",
      "price": 34800.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 30
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this meticulously maintained vehicle, a premier selection for the discerning driver. This unit exhibits a high degree of mechanical integrity and has been preserved to our exacting standards. Its performance profile remains robust, offering a sophisticated driving experience that balances reliability with prestige. Each component has been thoroughly inspected to ensure it meets our dealership's rigorous benchmarks for quality and long-term value.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 30
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Thanks so much for stopping by to check out my car. It\u2019s been a fantastic ride and has served me so well, but it\u2019s finally time to pass it along to someone new! It\u2019s in really solid shape, runs like a dream, and has been super well-maintained. Whether you're commuting or heading out on a road trip, this car is ready for it all. I'd love for it to go to a good home, so feel free to reach out if you have any questions or want to come take it for a spin!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 30
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Up for sale is a 2004 Porsche 911 Carrera (996.2) powered by the 3.6L M96 flat-six with VarioCam Plus, delivering a robust 320 hp to the rear wheels via a G96 6-speed manual gearbox. The drivetrain is solid, featuring a documented IMS bearing retrofit and a fresh clutch assembly. Suspension geometry is true, though the Bilstein dampers are seasoned. The exterior displays minor stone chipping on the front fascia and some patina on the 18-inch Carrera II wheels, consistent with a well-maintained driver. Inside, the leather retains its structural integrity with minimal bolster compression. A mechanically honest example for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 31500.0,
